Nova Pilbeam https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nova_Pilbeam 0 Nova Margery Pilbeam (15 November 1919 – 17 July 2015) was an English film and stage actress. She played leading roles in two Alfred Hitchcock movies of the 1930s, and made her last film in 1948. Nova_Margery_Pilbeam ( 15_November_1919 – 17_July_2015 ) was an_English_film_and_stage_actress .
